        "text": "<p>Please provide the following documentation to complete the full application:</p>\n<p>Diagram of the Farm including:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\">Dimensions&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\">Farm number locations</span><a href=\"https://www.coloradofingerprinting.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you do not have the map available at this point you will be provided the ability to upload them at a later time however, the Application will not be processed until all the information is provided and the application fees are paid.</p>",
